{"tid":1261869,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）研究一下律政司聲明","createTime":"2019-06-27T12:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T12:15:56.000Z","uid":230652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"600b06d9f38c712bd15573c2cadf866cbfb3adeb","tid":1261869,"uid":230652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:14:17.000Z","msg":"律政司發表聲明。<br />\n<br />\n對於有示威人士要求不檢控被捕示威者，發言人指，所有案件由執法機關調查，完成後有需要時才會交予律政司，獨立決定是否提出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就每宗案件的刑事檢控決定</span></strong></span>，律政司必須按證據、適用法律和《檢控守則》作出，如有充分證據進行檢控，律政司<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">會考慮作出檢控是否符合公眾利益，包括罪行的性質、嚴重程度及疑犯的態度或心理狀況等，</span></strong></span>無論任何人就任何事件如何定性，均不影響律政司的刑事檢控工作。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又呼籲示威者和平理性表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n律政司係咪打算同我地講有兩個方法救義士<br />\n1）如果警犬唔起訴 義士自然冇事<br />\n2）就算起訴左 可以利用公眾利益尼點黎救？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申（非法律JJ"},{"pid":"6ba1fa375b4bd15f949c5c8c998a3d3a2ea686f5","tid":1261869,"uid":230652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:14:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"719a9506fcc0a280992a1d302184bdb505cef32e","tid":1261869,"uid":230652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:14:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"368a9635d88da59f1728302c65e86144be301f03","tid":1261869,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"佢打算同你講我地會照做，吹咩"}]}